full_text: Diagnostic errors - Researchers: "Patients often felt that problematic interactions with clinicians played a big part in diagnostic errors...frequently reported being ignored or disrespected, or said clinicians didn’t communicate well with them." @statnews https://t.co/N7Cw3H8oXd
Hospitals and health centers should launch programs to formally collect patient reports and use that data to improve care and prevent patient harm. https://t.co/2VB0U4EXqF
